              <div class="step-number">4</div>
              <div class="step-content">
                <h3>Confirm Your Registration</h3>
                <p>After submitting the form, you will receive a confirmation email to the provided team leader's email address. Please follow the instructions in the email to confirm your registration.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="instruction-step">
              <div class="step-number">5</div>
              <div class="step-content">
                <h3>Attend the Orientation Session</h3>
                <p>You will be invited to attend a mandatory online orientation session, where the rules and details of the competition will be explained. Make sure all team members attend this session.</p>
